Cell["\<\
In the following circuit, there is a classical feedforward control of the \
second qubit depending on the outcome of the measurement on the first qubit. \
After the measurement, the first qubit is considered as a classical memory \
(or destroyed):\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->213767234,ExpressionUUID->"2fb5e8c0-11a5-458b-aa0c-0ea8f7e1ca09"],

