Cell["\<\
In some cases, mid-circuit measurement are used to coherently control other \
parts of quantum register depending on measurement outcome on some qubits. In \
this case, the measured qubits are still considered as quantum system, and \
hence it is natural to display the evolution of correspoinding qubits in \
solid lines:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->294322605,ExpressionUUID->"a1fcaac0-2ae7-47c4-b3bf-59a2571c88e8"],

